    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know if \"changing\" is possible when the essence is gone. if the artist is dead, then what's the point of the person? it feels like i'm just an empty vessel carrying around a corpse. it's exhausting to keep pretending there's something inside me when there truly isn't anything left.",
